Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 16:33:05 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] ADD clean-review completion prompts to close accepted
 patch chats

Clean review should hand control back to the reviewed patch-agent chat so the user can explicitly decide whether the feature is done. The controller records the reviewed commit for linearization, highlights the patch-agent chat, resolves yes/no answers locally, and keeps review marker parsing strict enough that contradictory FINDINGS before NO_FINDINGS still requires another fix round.
